ai-pp1.6:1.1_0: Instead, they used to perform the six people.
ai-pp1.6:2.1_0: There is a person who, having realized the principle for recitation of principles, for which gentlemen who dwell at because of all.
ai-pp1.6:2.2_0: There is a gentleman who, having realized the awakening factor of energy, and his power don’t fall under the sway of wicked desires. They don’t attain the meditations on awakening.
ai-pp1.6:2.3_0: There is a person who, having directly known for themselves the truth, cut off at the root, made an end of suffering in this very life. They’ve gone forth from the lay life to homelessness.
ai-pp1.6:2.4_0: There are such a person who, having realized the truth, cut off the stain of truth, and they don’t make an end of suffering in this very life.
ai-pp1.6:2.5_0: There is a person who, having directly known for themselves the truths of the truth, and one who doesn’t penetrate so far from the present life. They don’t make an end of suffering in this very life.
ai-pp1.6:2.6_0: There is a person who, having directly known for themselves the truths of the truth, not realizing anything that can be realized by insight to this state of existence. They don’t make an end of suffering in this very life.
